1
00:00:22,689 --> 00:00:26,026
Alam mo ba kung bakit sila ang pinili ko?

2
00:00:29,946 --> 00:00:33,783
Kung bakit sila ang pinili ko
para baguhin ang mundo?

3
00:00:34,617 --> 00:00:37,954
Dahil mahina sila.

4
00:00:39,456 --> 00:00:41,916
Marupok sila.

5
00:00:44,961 --> 00:00:46,963
Madaling baguhin.

6
00:00:47,589 --> 00:00:49,049
Madaling manipulahin.

7
00:00:51,217 --> 00:00:53,803
Mga perpektong kasangkapan.

8
00:00:57,891 --> 00:00:59,059
Anak.

9
00:00:59,142 --> 00:01:00,977
-Mama.
-Anak.

10
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:03,772
Hindi ko maintindihan. Paano mo…

11
00:01:03,855 --> 00:01:07,108
Sorcerer siya.
Sorcerer siya sa totoong buhay.

12
00:01:07,192 --> 00:01:08,234
Mike.

13
00:01:10,361 --> 00:01:12,781
Nagawa mo. Nagawa mo talaga.

14
00:01:15,617 --> 00:01:16,534
'Yong mga bata.

15
00:01:16,618 --> 00:01:18,787
Nakuha ni Vecna 'yong mga bata.

16
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:21,081
Kaya nga, e. Sina Derek, Mary, Glenn.

17
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,417
Hindi. Hindi lang sila.

18
00:01:26,377 --> 00:01:27,212
Pati 'yong iba,

19
00:01:27,295 --> 00:01:29,380
hindi sila nakalabas ng Hawkins.

20
00:01:31,049 --> 00:01:34,594
Natulungan ko sana silang lumaban
kung kumilos ako agad.

21
00:01:36,346 --> 00:01:37,388
Pero huli na 'ko.

22
00:01:38,765 --> 00:01:41,184
Kaya nakuha niya silang lahat.

23
00:01:42,143 --> 00:01:43,394
Lahat ng 12 bata.

24
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:47,107
Nabigo tayo.

25
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:49,567
Nabigo ako.

26
00:01:49,651 --> 00:01:50,485
Hindi.

27
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:57,951
Sa tunnels tayo. Radio Shack.

28
00:02:47,041 --> 00:02:51,337
Alam ko na magulo ang alaala n'yo
kung pa'no kayo napunta dito.

29
00:02:52,338 --> 00:02:53,339
-Mary!
-Nalilito kayo.

30
00:02:53,423 --> 00:02:54,340
Holly!

31
00:02:54,424 --> 00:02:56,968
Sinubukan kayong kunin ng mga halimaw.

32
00:02:57,051 --> 00:02:57,927
Hi!

33
00:02:58,511 --> 00:03:00,305
Pero nailigtas ko kayo.

34
00:03:00,388 --> 00:03:01,764
-Kumusta na?
-Ayos lang.

35
00:03:01,848 --> 00:03:02,891
Ang lugar na 'to,

36
00:03:03,474 --> 00:03:04,475
itong bahay ko,

37
00:03:05,101 --> 00:03:06,477
bahay n'yo na rin.

38
00:03:07,187 --> 00:03:08,354
Ligtas kayo dito.

39
00:03:08,938 --> 00:03:11,691
Basta't hindi kayo pupunta sa gubat,
sa bahay ng mga halimaw,

40
00:03:11,774 --> 00:03:13,484
walang mangyayari sa inyo.

41
00:03:13,568 --> 00:03:16,571
Alam kong iniisip ng karamihan sa inyo

42
00:03:16,654 --> 00:03:19,574
kung kailan susunod dito
ang mga kaibigan at pamilya n'yo.

43
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:24,204
Sa totoo lang, mas marami pang nakataya
kesa sa buhay ng mga minamahal n'yo.

44
00:03:26,289 --> 00:03:27,999
Ayoko kayong takutin.

45
00:03:28,917 --> 00:03:31,502
Pero alam kong may tapang kayo
na harapin ang totoo.

46
00:03:32,086 --> 00:03:35,632
May masamang kadiliman na kumakalat
hindi lang sa Hawkins,

47
00:03:35,715 --> 00:03:36,925
kundi sa buong mundo,

48
00:03:37,008 --> 00:03:40,553
at di magtatagal,
magiging huli na para pigilan 'to.

49
00:03:40,637 --> 00:03:44,849
Itong kadiliman na 'to,
para siyang Black Thing sa libro n'yo.

50
00:03:44,933 --> 00:03:47,227
Kung ano'ng banta ng Black Thing
sa pamilya ni Meg,

51
00:03:47,310 --> 00:03:49,270
gano'n din ang kadiliman sa pamilya n'yo,

52
00:03:49,354 --> 00:03:52,190
pero may paraan ako para matalo 'to.

53
00:03:52,273 --> 00:03:53,483
Pa'no?

54
00:03:55,109 --> 00:03:59,530
Malayo at mahaba na ang nilakbay ko
sa kabilang dimensiyon.

55
00:04:00,114 --> 00:04:02,659
Sa paglalakbay ko,
may natuklasan akong panibagong mundo.

56
00:04:03,743 --> 00:04:05,245
Mundong malayo sa Earth.

57
00:04:05,328 --> 00:04:08,706
Kapareho lang din siya
ng mundo natin, pero…

58
00:04:09,624 --> 00:04:10,708
mas maganda.

59
00:04:11,459 --> 00:04:13,294
Walang halimaw at kadiliman.

60
00:04:14,712 --> 00:04:15,838
'Yon ang liwanag.

61
00:04:16,422 --> 00:04:19,342
At 'yon ang totoong dahilan
kung bakit kayo ang pinili ko.

62
00:04:19,842 --> 00:04:23,263
Bukod-tangi kayong mga bata.

63
00:04:23,846 --> 00:04:26,057
Gaya ni Meg, espesyal din kayo.

64
00:04:27,058 --> 00:04:29,060
May natutulog kayong kapangyarihan dito.

65
00:04:30,144 --> 00:04:31,688
At kung magtutulungan tayo,

66
00:04:31,771 --> 00:04:33,940
kaya nating gisingin
ang kapangyarihang 'yon.

67
00:04:34,023 --> 00:04:37,193
Gamit ang lakas natin, dadalhin natin
ang mundong 'yon sa mundo natin.

68
00:04:37,277 --> 00:04:41,781
At habang papalapit ang liwanag
sa kadiliman,

69
00:04:42,365 --> 00:04:44,117
tatabunan ng liwanag ang kadiliman,

70
00:04:44,701 --> 00:04:47,078
maililigtas natin ang mga mahal n'yo,
at kayo…

71
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:50,623
ang magiging tagapagligtas.

72
00:04:55,378 --> 00:04:56,963
Ano 'yon, Holly?

73
00:04:57,755 --> 00:05:00,091
Aalis ka ba ulit?

74
00:05:01,009 --> 00:05:03,594
Para magdala ng mga espesyal na bata dito?

75
00:05:03,678 --> 00:05:04,929
Kawawa si Holly.

76
00:05:05,013 --> 00:05:08,850
Siya ang una kong pinili
kaya naiwan siyang mag-isa dito.

77
00:05:08,933 --> 00:05:11,561
Pero wag kang mag-alala,
hindi na kita iiwan.

78
00:05:12,395 --> 00:05:14,063
Hindi ko na kayo iiwan kahit kailan.

79
00:05:14,647 --> 00:05:15,648
Pero sa ngayon,

80
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:18,484
kumain at maglaro muna kayo.

81
00:05:19,527 --> 00:05:21,446
Higit sa lahat, magpahinga kayo.

82
00:05:22,447 --> 00:05:23,489
Dahil bukas…

83
00:05:25,783 --> 00:05:27,160
Bukas, magsisimula na.

84
00:07:01,379 --> 00:07:02,880
Sabi mo walang lumabas dito.

85
00:07:02,964 --> 00:07:04,966
Sabi ng Sec walang lumabas o pumasok.

86
00:07:05,049 --> 00:07:06,843
Ano, naglaho sila na parang si Houdini?

87
00:07:06,926 --> 00:07:07,969
Di ko alam, sir.

88
00:07:08,052 --> 00:07:10,179
Galugarin n'yo
ang bawat sulok ng building.

89
00:07:10,263 --> 00:07:14,225
Bawat kuwarto, vent, access panel.
Sige na. Kilos na! Kilos na!

90
00:07:52,054 --> 00:07:52,972
Okay ka lang?

91
00:07:53,055 --> 00:07:55,224
Nawala ako.

92
00:07:56,184 --> 00:07:57,560
Masyado tayong malayo.

93
00:07:57,643 --> 00:08:00,855
Ayos lang. Malayo na tayo.
Di na nila tayo mahahabol.

94
00:08:00,938 --> 00:08:02,482
Ang galing no'ng gimik mo.

95
00:08:03,608 --> 00:08:06,402
Ah, hindi, astigin pala ang tawag do'n.

96
00:08:07,153 --> 00:08:09,655
Di ba 'yon ang dinagdag mo
sa vocabulary ni El?

97
00:08:10,239 --> 00:08:13,367
Bad influence ako.

98
00:08:13,451 --> 00:08:15,703
Kaya nga, parehas pala tayo.

99
00:08:30,927 --> 00:08:32,678
-Lucas?
-Hala ka.

100
00:08:32,762 --> 00:08:34,514
-Naku po.
-Uy. Uy, guys.

101
00:08:34,597 --> 00:08:36,766
-Naku po.
-Uy.

102
00:08:36,849 --> 00:08:37,683
Putsa.

103
00:08:37,767 --> 00:08:39,060
Gasgas lang 'to.

104
00:08:39,143 --> 00:08:41,395
-Diyos ko, Mike, first aid nga.
-Putsa!

105
00:08:41,479 --> 00:08:43,105
Tingnan natin.

106
00:08:43,189 --> 00:08:44,899
-Pakiangat nga. Patingin kami.
-Sige.

107
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:49,820
Di naman masyadong malala, e.

108
00:08:49,904 --> 00:08:50,947
'Tang ina.

109
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:55,159
Oo, sakto lang 'yan,
may dalawang malupit na peklat ka na.

110
00:08:55,243 --> 00:08:57,370
Sorry, di ko naprotektahan 'yong mga bata.

111
00:08:57,453 --> 00:09:01,290
Ginawa mo ang lahat.
Lumaban ka. Tinaya mo 'yong buhay mo.

112
00:09:01,374 --> 00:09:02,416
Galing ng hampas mo, a.

113
00:09:04,293 --> 00:09:05,294
Nakita mo 'yon?

114
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,213
Di lang niya nakita.

115
00:09:09,298 --> 00:09:14,303
Bale, no'ng lumutang 'yong Demos,
nabali 'yong katawan nila, namatay sila,

116
00:09:14,387 --> 00:09:16,389
kagagawan mo lahat 'yon?

117
00:09:16,472 --> 00:09:19,141
Oo… parang gano'n na nga.

118
00:09:19,225 --> 00:09:20,309
Putsa.

119
00:09:21,727 --> 00:09:22,853
Putsa.

120
00:09:22,937 --> 00:09:24,897
Alam mo ba'ng ibig sabihin no'n?

121
00:09:24,981 --> 00:09:27,942
Ikaw si Will the Wise, sa totoong buhay.

122
00:09:28,025 --> 00:09:30,778
-Hindi rin.
-Hindi siya wizard, sorcerer siya.

123
00:09:30,861 --> 00:09:33,239
Okay, sige, basta.

124
00:09:33,322 --> 00:09:35,241
Pero gets n'yo naman ako, di ba?

125
00:09:35,324 --> 00:09:37,702
Mag-iiba na ang takbo ng laban dito.

126
00:09:37,785 --> 00:09:39,120
May pangalawang El na tayo.

127
00:09:39,203 --> 00:09:41,998
Hindi ako pangalawang El.
Wala akong powers.

128
00:09:42,081 --> 00:09:44,917
Nakikihigop lang ako.
Ninanakaw ko 'yong kay Vecna.

129
00:09:45,001 --> 00:09:47,461
Para magawa 'yon,
dapat malapit ako sa hive mind,

130
00:09:47,545 --> 00:09:48,879
kaso di na babalik si Vecna.

131
00:09:48,963 --> 00:09:50,923
-Baka bumalik 'yong Demos niya.
-Malabo.

132
00:09:51,007 --> 00:09:53,259
Mga bata ang habol nila
at hawak na sila ni Vecna,

133
00:09:53,342 --> 00:09:55,845
nasa kanya na 'yong mga kasangkapan niya.

134
00:09:59,724 --> 00:10:00,725
"Mga kasangkapan"?

135
00:10:00,808 --> 00:10:03,144
'Yon ang sabi niya.

136
00:10:03,227 --> 00:10:06,147
"Mga kasangkapan para baguhin ang mundo."

137
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:08,190
Sana lang mali 'yong theory mo.

138
00:10:09,108 --> 00:10:10,026
Anong theory?

139
00:10:10,943 --> 00:10:12,069
November 6.

140
00:10:13,321 --> 00:10:15,239
Sa araw kung sa'n nagsimula ang lahat,

141
00:10:16,532 --> 00:10:17,742
doon din matatapos lahat.

142
00:10:22,371 --> 00:10:23,372
Ayos ka lang?

143
00:10:28,753 --> 00:10:31,797
Sige, Lucas, dahan-dahan lang.

144
00:10:31,881 --> 00:10:34,175
Tulungan na kita. Tulungan na kita.

145
00:10:35,217 --> 00:10:36,802
Sige lang 'tol. Isa na lang.

146
00:10:36,886 --> 00:10:38,971
Uy. Halika nga.

147
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:44,894
May paraan pa kaya
para makakonekta tayo sa hive mind

148
00:10:44,977 --> 00:10:46,604
at magamit natin 'yong powers niya?

149
00:10:46,687 --> 00:10:48,439
Imposible 'yon, puwera na lang kung—

150
00:10:48,522 --> 00:10:50,483
Alam kong sarado na 'yong hive.

151
00:10:51,192 --> 00:10:52,610
Pero 'yong nangyari kanina,

152
00:10:52,693 --> 00:10:54,737
di rin naman natin naisip
na posible 'yon, e.

153
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:55,821
Ma.

154
00:10:56,364 --> 00:10:57,990
Ang akin lang, pa'no kung…

155
00:10:58,074 --> 00:11:02,828
Pa'no kung hindi mo gamitin
'yong powers niya sa mga alagad niya?

156
00:11:02,912 --> 00:11:06,666
Pa'no kaya kung sa kanya mo gamitin,
kay Vecna?

157
00:11:06,749 --> 00:11:08,668
Gisahin mo siya sa sarili niyang mantika.

158
00:11:08,751 --> 00:11:10,878
Di ka nabigo kanina.

159
00:11:11,921 --> 00:11:13,214
'Yong ipinamalas mo…

160
00:11:14,173 --> 00:11:16,133
ibang klase 'yon.

161
00:11:16,967 --> 00:11:18,761
Ikaw na mismo ang nagsabi.

162
00:11:18,844 --> 00:11:22,431
Pinili ka ni Vecna
dahil mahina ang tingin niya sa 'yo.

163
00:11:23,057 --> 00:11:25,476
'Yon din ang akala namin.
'Yon ang akala ko.

164
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:29,563
At 'yon ang pagkakamali
na hinding-hindi ko na uulitin.

165
00:11:30,314 --> 00:11:33,651
Pero sigurado ako na uulitin niya 'yon.

166
00:11:33,734 --> 00:11:35,319
At pag ginawa niya 'yon,

167
00:11:35,403 --> 00:11:39,573
'yon na ang huling pagkakamali
na gagawin ng tarantadong 'yon.

168
00:11:53,462 --> 00:11:56,132
Himala na nakabalik tayo nang buo.

169
00:11:57,049 --> 00:12:01,470
Sana masabi ko rin 'yon
sa pinakamamahal na BMW ni Harrington.

170
00:12:02,805 --> 00:12:04,557
Talaga ba?

171
00:12:05,057 --> 00:12:07,309
Parang walang nangyari, a?
Nakuha mo pang magbiro.

172
00:12:11,856 --> 00:12:14,316
Hahanapin mo si Vecna, ta's uuwi ka.
'Yon ang plano.

173
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,444
-Pero di totoo 'yon, 'no?
-Totoo 'yon.

174
00:12:16,527 --> 00:12:19,405
Puro ka kasinungalingan.
Kagaya ng ginawa mo sa training ko.

175
00:12:19,488 --> 00:12:21,073
Ayaw mo akong isama sa crawls

176
00:12:21,157 --> 00:12:23,701
kasi plano mong patayin si Vecna
nang mag-isa at mamatay.

177
00:12:23,784 --> 00:12:27,371
Uy. Makinig ka nga.
Ibang kaso 'yong nangyari kanina.

178
00:12:27,455 --> 00:12:29,540
Dahil sa kryptonite, di ka makalaban.

179
00:12:29,623 --> 00:12:30,958
Wala na 'kong ibang magawa.

180
00:12:31,041 --> 00:12:32,001
E, 'yong bomba?

181
00:12:32,668 --> 00:12:35,504
Fail-safe lang 'yong bomba.

182
00:12:35,588 --> 00:12:38,340
Fail-safe na ikaw lang ang nakakaalam.

183
00:12:40,217 --> 00:12:42,136
Nakita ko sa mga mata mo kanina.

184
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:44,805
Nakita ko.

185
00:12:46,223 --> 00:12:48,100
Handa ka nang mamatay.

186
00:12:51,187 --> 00:12:52,646
At lagi kang gano'n.

187
00:12:55,733 --> 00:12:56,734
Uy!

188
00:12:57,359 --> 00:12:59,820
Akala ko ba nandito
'yong mga kaibigan n'yo?

189
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:13,834
Anak ng tokwa naman, o.

190
00:13:31,936 --> 00:13:33,687
Ayos. Astig nito, ha.

191
00:13:33,771 --> 00:13:34,939
Nasa lobby tayo.

192
00:13:35,564 --> 00:13:39,318
Sa'n ba talaga tayo pupunta?

193
00:13:39,401 --> 00:13:42,530
Oo nga. Ano ba'ng hinahanap natin?

194
00:13:42,613 --> 00:13:44,448
Napanood n'yo 'yong Return of the Jedi?

195
00:13:44,532 --> 00:13:46,283
-'Yong may teddy bears?
-Ewoks 'yon.

196
00:13:46,367 --> 00:13:47,535
Oo, the best 'yon.

197
00:13:47,618 --> 00:13:48,452
-Talaga?
-Totoo ba?

198
00:13:48,536 --> 00:13:51,163
Hindi, pero gusto ng mga bata 'yon,
kaya benta sa kanya.

199
00:13:51,247 --> 00:13:54,875
Di ba do'n sa film, dapat masira ng Rebels
'yong pangalawang Death Star,

200
00:13:54,959 --> 00:13:57,127
kaso may protective energy shield 'yon

201
00:13:57,211 --> 00:13:59,046
na gawa ng isang shield generator.

202
00:13:59,129 --> 00:14:02,299
Ayos. Salamat sa pag-summarize ng movie
na napanood na namin.

203
00:14:02,383 --> 00:14:04,468
May kaugnayan kasi 'yong movie, Steve.

204
00:14:05,052 --> 00:14:09,557
Tingin ko itong malamang pader na 'to
ang version ni Vecna ng energy shield,

205
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:11,267
'yon nga lang, hindi 'to sci-fi.

206
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:15,271
Supernatural 'to
na gawa ng dark magic ni Vecna.

207
00:14:15,354 --> 00:14:19,567
Dark magic shield ang pumipigil sa 'tin
na matunton siya at mailigtas si Holly.

208
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:20,901
Kung tama ang tantiya ko,

209
00:14:20,985 --> 00:14:23,028
nandito sa lab 'yong shield generator.

210
00:14:23,112 --> 00:14:27,283
-Kung mahahanap natin 'yong generator…
-Masisira natin 'yong pader.

211
00:14:27,366 --> 00:14:29,702
-Huli si Vecna, ligtas si Holly.
-At may medal tayo.

212
00:14:29,785 --> 00:14:31,370
Ano naman ang itsura no'n?

213
00:14:31,453 --> 00:14:33,163
Pa'no ko malalaman?

214
00:14:49,138 --> 00:14:50,139
Taas o baba?

215
00:14:51,348 --> 00:14:53,934
Parehas. Magdalawang grupo tayo.
Para mas malawak.

216
00:14:54,018 --> 00:14:57,062
Game ako d'yan,
pero puwede bang lumipat ng team?

217
00:14:57,146 --> 00:14:58,856
Nance, sa taas tayo?

218
00:14:58,939 --> 00:15:00,482
-Ano…
-Seryoso ka ba?

219
00:15:00,566 --> 00:15:02,276
Kailangan namin ni Dustin ng space.

220
00:15:02,359 --> 00:15:03,193
-Please.
-Please.

221
00:15:03,277 --> 00:15:04,486
Sige. E di tayong dalawa.

222
00:15:04,570 --> 00:15:05,905
Kailangan din natin ng space.

223
00:15:05,988 --> 00:15:08,616
Lahat na lang, puwera kay Nancy.
Galing mo naman.

224
00:15:08,699 --> 00:15:11,368
Oy, wala tayong oras sa ganyan.

225
00:15:11,452 --> 00:15:13,245
Para madali, walang lipatan.

226
00:15:13,329 --> 00:15:14,538
-Nance, hindi ko—
-Di ko—

227
00:15:14,622 --> 00:15:15,456
Tapos ang usapan.

228
00:15:18,459 --> 00:15:19,668
Saya naman.

229
00:15:22,963 --> 00:15:24,173
Saya talaga.

230
00:15:42,733 --> 00:15:44,777
Eto na 'ko!

231
00:15:49,949 --> 00:15:50,991
Taya!

232
00:15:52,451 --> 00:15:53,869
Lagot ka sa 'kin!

233
00:15:54,662 --> 00:15:57,164
Grabe, buong araw ka dito, tapos wala ako.

234
00:15:57,247 --> 00:16:00,834
Ano sa tingin mo? Di ako sure, e.
Bagay ba sa 'kin ang green?

235
00:16:02,544 --> 00:16:04,421
Oo, bagay na bagay.

236
00:16:05,631 --> 00:16:07,800
-Ano ba'ng meron?
-Wala.

237
00:16:07,883 --> 00:16:09,176
Iba 'yong kinikilos mo.

238
00:16:09,259 --> 00:16:13,555
Nakarami yata ako ng kain ng cake, e.

239
00:16:13,639 --> 00:16:16,183
May tsaa naman siguro si Mr. Whatsit, 'no?

240
00:16:16,266 --> 00:16:18,727
Sigurado 'yon. Lahat naman meron siya, e.

241
00:16:39,915 --> 00:16:41,500
-Ano'ng ginagawa mo?
-Usap tayo.

242
00:16:41,583 --> 00:16:44,086
-Holly, ang plano—
-Pagkaalis ni Henry. Alam ko.

243
00:16:44,169 --> 00:16:46,463
Pero kinikilabutan ako
sa mga sinasabi niya.

244
00:16:46,547 --> 00:16:50,426
-May nakakita ba sa 'yo dito?
-Hindi, nag-ingat ako. Makinig ka muna.

245
00:16:50,509 --> 00:16:51,969
Alam ko kung ba't kami kinidnap.

246
00:16:52,052 --> 00:16:56,640
Gagamitin kami ni Henry
para dalhin ang isa pang mundo sa Earth.

247
00:16:56,724 --> 00:16:59,018
"Dalhin ang isa pang mundo"?
Di ko maintindihan.

248
00:16:59,101 --> 00:17:02,771
Para daw iligtas ang Earth,
pero tingin ko sisirain niya, e.

249
00:17:02,855 --> 00:17:05,107
Kung anumang plano niya,
gagawin na niya bukas.

250
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:07,317
Umalis na tayo ng Camazotz, ngayon na.

251
00:17:07,401 --> 00:17:10,154
Di tayo makakaalis.
Dahil pag nalaman niya na wala ka,

252
00:17:10,237 --> 00:17:12,740
matutunton ka ng powers niya
tapos mahuhuli niya tayo.

253
00:17:15,117 --> 00:17:17,161
-Sigurado kang walang nakakita sa 'yo?
-Oo.

254
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:31,341
Sino ka, ha?

255
00:17:31,425 --> 00:17:32,760
Derek. Ikaw, sino ka?

256
00:17:32,843 --> 00:17:34,595
Ano'ng ginagawa mo dito, damulag?

257
00:17:34,678 --> 00:17:37,222
Di na 'ko si Derek Damulag.
Ako na si Dakilang Derek.

258
00:17:37,306 --> 00:17:38,474
-May narinig ka?
-Kaunti.

259
00:17:38,557 --> 00:17:42,019
Gusto n'yong tumakas pero di puwede
dahil dapat munang umalis ni Henry,

260
00:17:42,102 --> 00:17:44,396
kung hindi, mahahanap kayo
ng evil magic ni Vecna.

261
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:46,774
"Vecna"? Di ko sinabi 'yon.
Pa'no mo nalaman 'yon?

262
00:17:46,857 --> 00:17:48,317
-Mike.
-Mike?

263
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,234
'Yong kapatid ko?

264
00:17:49,318 --> 00:17:52,071
-Mag-best friend na kami.
-Best friend mo si Mike?

265
00:17:52,154 --> 00:17:55,199
Pati sina Will at Lucas at Erica
at Mrs. Byers at Miss Robin.

266
00:17:55,282 --> 00:17:57,701
Niligtas namin 'yong iba, pero wala rin.
Kaya eto ako.

267
00:17:57,785 --> 00:17:58,994
Akala ko mag-isa na 'ko,

268
00:17:59,078 --> 00:18:02,915
pero nakita kita kanina at naisip ko,
"Alam ni Holly na nanggagago siya."

269
00:18:02,998 --> 00:18:06,335
Kaya sinundan kita sa gubat
at tama nga ang kutob ko.

270
00:18:06,418 --> 00:18:07,419
Puwedeng sumama?

271
00:18:07,503 --> 00:18:10,798
Hindi! Walang aalis, okay?
Hangga't nakabantay si Henry.

272
00:18:11,548 --> 00:18:13,217
E, kung siguraduhin nating hindi?

273
00:18:14,259 --> 00:18:15,803
Di ka puwedeng sumama.

274
00:18:17,054 --> 00:18:19,264
Pero matutulungan mo kaming tumakas.

275
00:18:19,348 --> 00:18:24,228
Pero tama na muna 'yang "Dakila" na 'yan.

276
00:18:24,311 --> 00:18:25,938
Para magawa namin 'to,

277
00:18:26,021 --> 00:18:27,815
kailangan namin si Derek Damulag.

278
00:18:32,069 --> 00:18:34,029
Okay, simple lang 'yong goal.

279
00:18:34,113 --> 00:18:36,323
Ilalapit natin si Will sa hive mind.

280
00:18:36,406 --> 00:18:40,035
Pag malapit na siya, kokonekta siya ulit.

281
00:18:40,119 --> 00:18:42,371
Pero hindi na Demo ang target niya ngayon.

282
00:18:42,454 --> 00:18:44,498
Si Vecna na.

283
00:18:44,581 --> 00:18:46,416
Isang hataw lang, patay siya,

284
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:50,295
tapos na siya, ang mga kampon niya,
at ang bangungot na 'to.

285
00:18:51,255 --> 00:18:52,381
Ayun lang. So…

286
00:18:53,298 --> 00:18:54,925
Ano sa tingin n'yo? Ano?

287
00:18:55,884 --> 00:18:58,011
May ideas kayo? Ano sa palagay n'yo?

288
00:18:58,095 --> 00:18:59,513
Walang masamang idea.

289
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:03,433
Tingin ko maganda naman 'yong plano.

290
00:19:04,476 --> 00:19:06,812
Maganda naman, di ba?

291
00:19:06,895 --> 00:19:07,896
Uy.

292
00:19:09,231 --> 00:19:10,899
Oo, hindi. Oo…

293
00:19:11,567 --> 00:19:12,818
Maganda 'yong plano.

294
00:19:12,901 --> 00:19:14,153
Kaya lang…

295
00:19:14,236 --> 00:19:15,320
Kaya lang…

296
00:19:15,404 --> 00:19:17,906
Will, napatay mo 'yong Demo
gamit 'yong isip mo?

297
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:19,491
-Ano…
-Tatlong Demos.

298
00:19:19,575 --> 00:19:20,784
Nang sabay-sabay.

299
00:19:20,868 --> 00:19:23,036
Aba, petmalu naman pala talaga!

300
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:24,413
Wizard ka nga talaga.

301
00:19:24,496 --> 00:19:26,582
Sorcerer siya. 'Yong powers niya–

302
00:19:26,665 --> 00:19:27,916
Likas. Oo, salamat.

303
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:28,876
Mahalaga ba 'yon?

304
00:19:28,959 --> 00:19:30,127
-Mahalaga.
-Mahalaga.

305
00:19:30,210 --> 00:19:32,462
Puwede bang mag-focus na tayo?

306
00:19:33,130 --> 00:19:34,798
Sige, ako muna.

307
00:19:37,217 --> 00:19:41,054
Puwede tayong gumawa
ng isa pang telemetry ek-ek na 'yon.

308
00:19:41,138 --> 00:19:45,976
Para mahanap natin si El,
si Jonathan saka 'yong iba,

309
00:19:46,059 --> 00:19:47,978
baka-sakaling nahanap na nila si Vecna.

310
00:19:48,061 --> 00:19:51,148
Si Dustin 'yong gumawa ng tracker.
Di ko alam kung pa'no 'yon.

311
00:19:51,231 --> 00:19:53,859
Puwede tayong magtulungan,
isipin natin kung pa'no gawin,

312
00:19:53,942 --> 00:19:55,277
pero aabutin 'yon ng…

313
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:57,154
Ilang araw, at wala tayo no'n.

314
00:19:57,237 --> 00:20:00,991
Isakay kaya natin si Will sa van
ta's ilibot natin siya na parang antenna?

315
00:20:01,074 --> 00:20:02,743
-Ano?
-Walang masamang idea, di ba?

316
00:20:02,826 --> 00:20:04,328
Sige, ano pa?

317
00:20:04,912 --> 00:20:06,663
Dali, ano pa?

318
00:20:06,747 --> 00:20:07,915
Kahit ano.

319
00:20:08,749 --> 00:20:09,708
Kahit ano.

320
00:20:10,751 --> 00:20:12,127
May nagugutom din ba sa inyo?

321
00:20:22,638 --> 00:20:23,639
Bugles?

322
00:20:23,722 --> 00:20:25,265
Magugunaw na 'yong mundo.

323
00:20:25,349 --> 00:20:28,310
Kaya nga. Kailangan ng utak ng tao
ng lakas at sustansiya

324
00:20:28,393 --> 00:20:29,895
para laging focused at creative.

325
00:20:31,605 --> 00:20:32,439
Kain na.

326
00:21:02,886 --> 00:21:05,264
-Alam ko na, guys!
-Alam ko na!

327
00:21:05,347 --> 00:21:06,932
Okay, ako muna.

328
00:21:07,015 --> 00:21:11,812
Wala si Dustin,
pero 'yong mentor niya, nandito.

329
00:21:11,895 --> 00:21:14,356
-Mr. Clarke?
-Siya ang pinakamalaking nerd sa Hawkins.

330
00:21:14,439 --> 00:21:16,233
Siya ang nagturo kay Dustin.

331
00:21:16,316 --> 00:21:19,486
Kung may makakagawa ng bagong tracker
nang mabilisan, siya 'yon.

332
00:21:19,569 --> 00:21:20,946
Puwede rin.

333
00:21:21,029 --> 00:21:23,699
Oo, pero matatagalan 'yon.

334
00:21:23,782 --> 00:21:27,327
'Yong plano ko, mas mabilis,
mas malupit, at mas maganda.

335
00:21:28,370 --> 00:21:31,915
No'ng iniinit ko 'tong popcorn,
naalala ko si Billy sa sauna.

336
00:21:31,999 --> 00:21:35,627
Pinainitan natin siya
para gisingin 'yong particles, di ba?

337
00:21:35,711 --> 00:21:38,547
Natutulog 'yon, kagaya ng kernels na 'to,

338
00:21:38,630 --> 00:21:41,717
kagaya ng particles
sa loob ng Demos na pinatay ni Will.

339
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:43,844
Para mabuhay 'yon, kailangang painitan.

340
00:21:43,927 --> 00:21:46,805
May 50,000 watts na dumadaloy
sa tower na 'yon.

341
00:21:48,557 --> 00:21:52,352
Kukuryentehin natin 'yong Demos,
bubuhayin natin 'yong particles,

342
00:21:52,436 --> 00:21:56,440
at voilà, may instant hive mind na tayo.

343
00:21:56,523 --> 00:21:58,775
Gusto mong i-Dr. Frankenstein
'yong patay na Demo?

344
00:21:58,859 --> 00:22:00,068
'Yan na 'yong big idea mo?

345
00:22:00,152 --> 00:22:02,571
-Mabagal 'yong plano mo.
-Katangahan 'yong plano mo.

346
00:22:02,654 --> 00:22:04,489
Oy, mga bata, awat na!

347
00:22:04,573 --> 00:22:05,866
Kaklaruhin ko lang.

348
00:22:05,949 --> 00:22:09,578
Parehong may butas ang idea n'yo.
Maraming butas.

349
00:22:09,661 --> 00:22:11,288
Kaya subukan natin pareho.

350
00:22:11,913 --> 00:22:14,875
Maghagis tayo ng dalawang dart
at baka-sakaling may masapol tayo.

351
00:22:29,473 --> 00:22:31,850
Ang daming hagdan, a.

352
00:22:33,101 --> 00:22:36,646
Sa kailaliman talaga ng dungeon
nakatago ang treasure.

353
00:22:38,315 --> 00:22:41,568
Ano ba talaga,
treasure o magic shield generator?

354
00:22:41,651 --> 00:22:43,779
Ayusin mo naman 'yong metaphors mo.

355
00:22:44,321 --> 00:22:45,280
Analogy 'yon.

356
00:22:55,999 --> 00:22:57,125
Okay.

357
00:22:57,751 --> 00:23:01,338
Di ko inasahan na may daycare
sa impiyernong 'to.

358
00:23:01,421 --> 00:23:02,547
Ayos 'to.

359
00:23:04,591 --> 00:23:06,468
Putsa, Henderson.

360
00:23:06,551 --> 00:23:07,594
Tama ka.

361
00:23:11,098 --> 00:23:12,057
Treasure nga.

362
00:23:14,643 --> 00:23:16,228
-Alam mo?
-Ano?

363
00:23:16,311 --> 00:23:19,231
Perfect ka dito dahil stuck sa level 1
ang development mo.

364
00:23:19,314 --> 00:23:22,984
Habang naghahanap ako sa basement,
maglaro ka muna ng bola dito.

365
00:23:23,068 --> 00:23:24,277
Ayos, sige.

366
00:23:24,361 --> 00:23:26,863
-Sa wakas, nagustuhan ko rin ang plano mo.
-Mukha nga.

367
00:23:26,947 --> 00:23:29,574
Sige, good luck na lang
sa paghahanap ng treasure.

368
00:23:29,658 --> 00:23:30,992
Ay, shield generator pala.

369
00:23:31,076 --> 00:23:32,786
Ay, gawa-gawa lang pala 'yon.

370
00:23:32,869 --> 00:23:33,870
Salamat.

371
00:23:34,496 --> 00:23:37,040
Nag-aalala 'kong baka mali si Dustin
sa pagkakataong 'to.

372
00:23:39,584 --> 00:23:41,420
Walang kabuhay-buhay dito, e.

373
00:23:42,879 --> 00:23:46,716
Ewan ko ba. Parang lalo kasing lumalabo.

374
00:23:47,217 --> 00:23:48,718
Nandito na tayo, e.

375
00:23:49,845 --> 00:23:51,721
Kaya halughugin na natin.

376
00:23:58,019 --> 00:23:58,895
Uy.

377
00:24:01,356 --> 00:24:02,774
May nagawa ba 'ko…

378
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:05,444
para ano… para mainis ka?

379
00:24:05,527 --> 00:24:07,154
Ano ba'ng pinagsasasabi mo?

380
00:24:07,237 --> 00:24:09,364
-Ewan. May tono ka, e.
-Tono?

381
00:24:09,448 --> 00:24:10,657
-Oo.
-Okay.

382
00:24:10,740 --> 00:24:12,909
Ayan, ganyan. 'Yong tono.

383
00:24:12,993 --> 00:24:18,248
Oo, may tono na ngayon
kasi para kang tanga, e.

384
00:24:19,583 --> 00:24:22,544
Parang tanga din ba 'ko sa baba kanina?

385
00:24:22,627 --> 00:24:26,506
Ah, no'ng nagpataasan
na naman kayo ng ihi ni Steve?

386
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:31,052
O baka no'ng gusto kang makasama ni Steve
tapos nag-alangan ka.

387
00:24:31,136 --> 00:24:34,598
Ang sabi ko, walang lipatan.

388
00:24:35,223 --> 00:24:36,933
Oo, pero nag-alangan ka muna.

389
00:24:37,017 --> 00:24:38,185
Di ako nag-alangan.

390
00:24:38,268 --> 00:24:40,187
Kilala kita. Nag-alangan ka.

391
00:24:41,396 --> 00:24:44,399
Okay. E, ano kung nag-alangan ako
kahit hindi naman?

392
00:24:44,483 --> 00:24:46,109
Hindi na mahalaga 'yon.

393
00:24:46,193 --> 00:24:48,111
Nawawala 'yong kapatid ko.

394
00:24:48,195 --> 00:24:50,238
Oo, kaya nga mahalaga 'yon, e.

395
00:24:51,490 --> 00:24:53,867
Pagkatapos ng lahat ng nangyari,

396
00:24:53,950 --> 00:24:55,285
ng nangyayari,

397
00:24:55,368 --> 00:24:57,579
natatakot ako, Nancy, okay?

398
00:24:57,662 --> 00:24:59,414
Sobra 'kong natatakot.

399
00:24:59,498 --> 00:25:02,501
Hindi ko alam kung ano'ng meron sa kabila.

400
00:25:02,584 --> 00:25:04,127
Ang alam ko lang,

401
00:25:04,211 --> 00:25:06,963
para magkaroon tayo
ng tsansang makaligtas dito,

402
00:25:07,047 --> 00:25:08,757
kailangan nating maging team.

403
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:10,383
Gaya ng dati.

404
00:25:10,467 --> 00:25:14,054
-Team pa rin tayo.
-Hindi na, e.

405
00:25:15,222 --> 00:25:16,306
Hindi na ngayon.

406
00:25:16,389 --> 00:25:20,769
So, ano, dito pa tayo mag-aayos
ng relationship issues natin?

407
00:25:20,852 --> 00:25:24,231
-Sa Hawkins Lab? Sa Upside Down?
-Hindi. Hindi, Nancy.

408
00:25:24,314 --> 00:25:27,359
Gusto ko lang na tigilan mo na
ang pag‑iwas sa 'kin.

409
00:25:28,109 --> 00:25:29,528
Maging totoo ka sa 'kin.

410
00:25:30,111 --> 00:25:33,698
Bakit, gano'n ka ba?
Naging totoo ka ba sa 'kin?

411
00:25:35,450 --> 00:25:36,660
Oo.

412
00:25:36,743 --> 00:25:38,286
Oo, naging totoo ako sa 'yo.

413
00:25:39,204 --> 00:25:41,039
-Nag-alangan ka, e.
-Hindi kaya.

414
00:25:41,122 --> 00:25:44,501
Kilala kita, Jonathan.
Kasinglaki ng truck 'yong pag-aalangan mo.

415
00:26:39,097 --> 00:26:40,557
Ano'ng ginagawa mo?

416
00:26:41,182 --> 00:26:42,183
Jonathan!

417
00:26:45,979 --> 00:26:47,230
Ano 'to?

418
00:26:48,064 --> 00:26:49,608
Ano 'yan?

419
00:26:50,609 --> 00:26:53,862
Puwede ko pa bang bawiin 'yong sinabi ko
tungkol sa theory ni Dustin?

420
00:27:01,703 --> 00:27:04,998
Nancy, Jonathan, copy n'yo? Over.

421
00:27:06,082 --> 00:27:10,128
Nasa simbahan na kami. Nasaan na ba kayo?

422
00:27:10,211 --> 00:27:11,254
Copy n'yo?

423
00:27:13,173 --> 00:27:14,215
Jonathan!

424
00:27:15,258 --> 00:27:17,010
Nancy, copy n'yo?

425
00:27:18,219 --> 00:27:19,429
Ano ba kayo?

426
00:27:19,512 --> 00:27:22,057
Pagkatapos n'yong makarating
ng pulis mo dito,

427
00:27:22,724 --> 00:27:26,478
laking gulat mo siguro
na ako ang nakita mo imbes na si Henry.

428
00:27:26,561 --> 00:27:27,937
Sorry, Kali.

429
00:27:28,813 --> 00:27:31,066
Sorry kung ngayon lang kita nahanap.

430
00:27:31,733 --> 00:27:33,026
Di mo naman alam, e.

431
00:27:33,109 --> 00:27:36,613
May bathtub ako, may tangke ako sa bahay.

432
00:27:39,032 --> 00:27:41,368
Nakakaabot ako sa malayo, kahit dito.

433
00:27:42,577 --> 00:27:46,122
Natakot siguro ako na hanapin ka.

434
00:27:47,207 --> 00:27:49,542
Ga'no karami ang alam mo
tungkol kay Henry?

435
00:27:49,626 --> 00:27:52,337
Lahat, maliban sa…

436
00:27:54,464 --> 00:27:56,424
buhay pa pala siya.

437
00:27:57,842 --> 00:27:59,469
Tulungan mo akong hanapin siya,

438
00:28:00,553 --> 00:28:01,429
at patayin siya.

439
00:28:01,513 --> 00:28:02,472
Tapos?

440
00:28:02,555 --> 00:28:04,182
Matatapos na 'to.

441
00:28:04,265 --> 00:28:06,935
Puwede na tayong mabuhay.
Mabuhay nang totoo.

442
00:28:07,018 --> 00:28:08,520
Pangarap lang 'yan, Jane.

443
00:28:08,603 --> 00:28:10,105
Puwede namang hindi, e.

444
00:28:11,523 --> 00:28:14,734
Pinangarap ko rin 'yan.

445
00:28:15,443 --> 00:28:17,696
Pinangarap kong tapusin lahat ng 'to,

446
00:28:19,364 --> 00:28:20,490
na…

447
00:28:22,325 --> 00:28:24,327
magamot ko 'yong sugat natin.

448
00:28:31,459 --> 00:28:32,961
Pero natunton nila ako.

449
00:28:34,170 --> 00:28:35,797
Natunton nila ang mga kaibigan ko.

450
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:36,965
Wag!

451
00:28:37,549 --> 00:28:38,508
Pinatay sila.

452
00:28:40,093 --> 00:28:41,469
At kinuha nila ako.

453
00:29:25,013 --> 00:29:28,099
Hindi ko maintindihan
kung bakit buhay pa ako.

454
00:29:28,183 --> 00:29:33,104
Akala ko kinuha nila 'yong doktor na 'yon
para pahirapan ako.

455
00:29:33,688 --> 00:29:35,440
Pero di 'to tungkol sa paghihiganti.

456
00:29:36,274 --> 00:29:38,485
Kailangan ako ni Dr. Kay.

457
00:29:39,194 --> 00:29:41,905
Kailangan niya ang dugo ko.

458
00:29:42,781 --> 00:29:45,784
At walang katapusan
ang pangangailangan niya.

459
00:29:50,872 --> 00:29:54,459
Kuha lang siya nang kuha.

460
00:29:55,293 --> 00:30:00,381
Naisip ko pa nga na baka bampira siya.

461
00:30:02,258 --> 00:30:04,594
Di ko alam kung ga'no 'ko katagal do'n.

462
00:30:04,677 --> 00:30:06,638
Dinodroga nila ako.

463
00:30:07,222 --> 00:30:09,808
Ang alam ko lang,
kailangan kong makalabas.

464
00:30:10,391 --> 00:30:12,185
At ang daan lang palabas…

465
00:30:13,102 --> 00:30:14,187
ay kamatayan.

466
00:30:19,108 --> 00:30:21,903
Akala ni Dr. Kay
napigilan niya ang kakayahan ko

467
00:30:21,986 --> 00:30:26,366
gamit ang nakakarinding tunog niya.

468
00:30:32,330 --> 00:30:35,041
Pero di lahat ng kakayahan,
ginagamitan ng kapangyarihan.

469
00:30:47,428 --> 00:30:50,974
Kung alam ko lang kung ano
ang nasa likod ng pintong 'yon,

470
00:30:52,058 --> 00:30:53,935
hindi na sana ako umalis.

471
00:31:04,529 --> 00:31:06,823
-Naisip namin 'yon.
-Ginawa niya siguro.

472
00:31:06,906 --> 00:31:08,825
-Ano'ng ginagawa nila?
-Naglalaro ako ng…

473
00:31:08,908 --> 00:31:10,076
Umalis ka nga, damulag!

474
00:31:10,159 --> 00:31:11,911
Nabasa mo ang isip ko, bugok!

475
00:31:12,996 --> 00:31:16,374
Derek, ano'ng ginagawa mo?
Di puwedeng pumunta sa gubat.

476
00:31:16,457 --> 00:31:17,458
Bawal 'yan.

477
00:31:17,542 --> 00:31:21,254
Sino'ng nagsabi, si Mr. Rogers?
Sipsipin niya 'yong birdie ko!

478
00:31:24,048 --> 00:31:25,842
Mr. Whatsit! Mr. Whatsit!

479
00:31:25,925 --> 00:31:28,303
-Pumunta si Derek sa gubat!
-Mr. Whatsit!

480
00:31:33,808 --> 00:31:35,768
Pa'no kung mahuli ni Henry si Derek?

481
00:31:35,852 --> 00:31:38,313
Baka saktan siya? O baka mas malala pa?

482
00:31:38,396 --> 00:31:40,732
Basta makarating si Derek sa kuweba,
ligtas siya.

483
00:31:40,815 --> 00:31:42,400
Dapat kumagat si Henry sa pain.

484
00:31:42,483 --> 00:31:45,570
Ga'no katagal bago mahanap 'yong exit?

485
00:31:45,653 --> 00:31:46,988
Sana hindi matagal.

486
00:31:47,071 --> 00:31:49,824
Ginabayan ka kasi ng friend mong si Kate—

487
00:31:49,908 --> 00:31:53,328
Dalawang taon ko nang nililibot
'tong maze na 'to.

488
00:31:53,411 --> 00:31:54,454
Ako 'yong gabay natin.

489
00:31:54,537 --> 00:31:56,539
Hahanapin natin
ang unang alaala niya sa 'yo

490
00:31:56,623 --> 00:31:58,666
at susundan natin 'yon
no'ng gabing kinuha ka.

491
00:31:58,750 --> 00:32:02,253
Kung tama ako, nando'n 'yong exit
papunta sa totoong mundo.

492
00:32:03,087 --> 00:32:04,547
Makakatakas na tayo sa Camazotz.

493
00:32:04,631 --> 00:32:07,050
Makakatakas na tayo sa Camazotz.

494
00:32:23,942 --> 00:32:24,943
Alam mo…

495
00:32:25,026 --> 00:32:26,235
na-realize ko,

496
00:32:26,819 --> 00:32:29,072
at alam kong pinatagal ko pa
kaya ang awkward na,

497
00:32:29,781 --> 00:32:32,700
pero di pa kita napapasalamatan
sa pagligtas sa buhay ko.

498
00:32:32,784 --> 00:32:36,120
Alam mo na, medyo big deal kasi 'yon.

499
00:32:36,204 --> 00:32:37,205
Lalo na sa 'kin.

500
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,166
Walang anuman.

501
00:32:40,249 --> 00:32:43,211
Ako dapat ang magpasalamat sa 'yo.

502
00:32:43,294 --> 00:32:45,588
Sa 'kin? Para sa'n?

503
00:32:45,672 --> 00:32:49,634
Dahil kinuwento mo sa 'kin
'yong tungkol kay Tammy at sa buhay mo.

504
00:32:49,717 --> 00:32:51,511
Napakalaking…

505
00:32:52,261 --> 00:32:53,262
tulong no'n.

506
00:32:53,346 --> 00:32:55,723
Ako? Nagkuwento?

507
00:32:56,599 --> 00:32:57,934
Tapos malaking tulong?

508
00:32:58,017 --> 00:32:59,852
Sabihin mo nga 'yan sa nanay ko.

509
00:33:02,355 --> 00:33:03,231
So,

510
00:33:04,023 --> 00:33:07,568
pagkatapos no'ng kay Tammy

511
00:33:07,652 --> 00:33:10,613
at saka no'ng nalinawan ka dahil sa tape,

512
00:33:10,697 --> 00:33:13,783
do'n ba kayo nagsimula ni Vickie na—

513
00:33:13,866 --> 00:33:15,159
Hindi, a.

514
00:33:16,035 --> 00:33:19,288
Wala pa 'kong lakas ng loob
na kausapin si Vic no'n.

515
00:33:19,372 --> 00:33:21,499
Natanggap ko na 'yong sarili ko,

516
00:33:21,582 --> 00:33:25,336
pero 'yong i-share ko
'yong parte na 'yon ng sarili ko sa iba,

517
00:33:25,420 --> 00:33:26,671
ibang usapan na 'yon.

518
00:33:27,505 --> 00:33:28,965
Pero katagalan,

519
00:33:30,383 --> 00:33:32,719
nagawa ko rin, nasabi ko rin sa iba.

520
00:33:34,554 --> 00:33:35,805
Mukhang tapos na 'to.

521
00:33:37,515 --> 00:33:38,349
Pero…

522
00:33:39,267 --> 00:33:40,351
Sandali.

523
00:33:40,435 --> 00:33:42,020
Kanino mo sinabi?

524
00:33:42,520 --> 00:33:44,313
Obvious naman. Kay Steve.

525
00:33:44,897 --> 00:33:46,274
Teka, ano?

526
00:33:46,357 --> 00:33:49,193
Robin, naguguluhan ako.

527
00:33:49,277 --> 00:33:50,528
Ang sinasabi mo ba…

528
00:33:50,611 --> 00:33:52,697
'Yong Steve mo, si Steve—

529
00:33:52,780 --> 00:33:55,491
Steve "The Hair" Harrington,
'yong dati kong karibal.

530
00:33:57,535 --> 00:33:58,953
Okay, humanda ka, ha!

531
00:34:04,459 --> 00:34:05,334
Okay 'yan!

532
00:34:06,836 --> 00:34:08,463
Teka nga, Robin.

533
00:34:08,546 --> 00:34:11,549
Okay naman si Steve.
Kaso di ko magets. Para kasing—

534
00:34:11,632 --> 00:34:13,092
Nakakagulat, 'no?

535
00:34:13,676 --> 00:34:15,303
-Oo.
-Maniwala ka, alam ko.

536
00:34:15,386 --> 00:34:18,639
Kaka-inject lang kasi sa 'min no'n
ng truth serum ng evil Russians,

537
00:34:18,723 --> 00:34:21,267
parang liquid courage 'yon
na sabog sa steroids.

538
00:34:21,350 --> 00:34:23,561
Sa totoo lang, may drugs man o wala,

539
00:34:23,644 --> 00:34:28,399
'yong maamin mo 'yon sa iba
tapos matanggap ka nila, alam mo 'yon?

540
00:34:28,483 --> 00:34:30,359
Para 'kong nabunutan ng tinik.

541
00:34:31,444 --> 00:34:34,072
At kung di ko 'yon sinabi kay Steve,

542
00:34:34,155 --> 00:34:37,450
malamang di ako nagkalakas-loob
na ipagtapat 'yon kay Vickie

543
00:34:37,533 --> 00:34:39,535
at baka di ko rin 'yon masabi sa 'yo.

544
00:34:39,619 --> 00:34:41,829
Pangatlo ka pa lang sa sinabihan ko.

545
00:34:41,913 --> 00:34:44,499
Balak kong doblehin 'yon
bago matapos ang taon

546
00:34:44,582 --> 00:34:48,294
kung matatalo mo 'yong sorcerer,
at hindi tayo mamamatay.

547
00:34:50,505 --> 00:34:55,134
Meron ka pa bang truth serum diyan?

548
00:34:57,386 --> 00:34:58,387
Hala!

549
00:35:01,015 --> 00:35:02,016
Umatras ka!

550
00:35:07,271 --> 00:35:08,189
Dito 'yon.

551
00:35:08,272 --> 00:35:09,607
Dito ako nagising.

552
00:35:10,108 --> 00:35:13,986
Sige. Ngayon humanap ka
ng kahit ano na parang kakaiba.

553
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:14,904
Nakatago 'yon.

554
00:35:14,987 --> 00:35:16,489
Mahirap makita, pero…

555
00:35:17,448 --> 00:35:18,533
Ayun, o.

556
00:35:20,576 --> 00:35:22,411
Madali naman pala.

557
00:35:44,308 --> 00:35:45,685
Alaala lang 'to.

558
00:35:45,768 --> 00:35:48,312
Kung anuman 'yong nasa baba,
di ka niya masasaktan.

559
00:36:14,797 --> 00:36:16,924
Hindi ko magets. Halloween 'to, a.

560
00:36:17,717 --> 00:36:19,051
Di ko pa nakikilala si Henry.

561
00:36:19,135 --> 00:36:21,596
Di porke't di mo siya nakita,
wala na siya dito.

562
00:36:28,561 --> 00:36:29,687
Tandaan mo…

563
00:36:29,770 --> 00:36:30,813
Alaala lang 'to.

564
00:36:30,897 --> 00:36:31,898
Mm-hmm.

565
00:36:38,279 --> 00:36:40,448
May isa pang alaala na malapit dito.

566
00:36:41,199 --> 00:36:43,242
Kailan mo talaga unang nakilala si Henry?

567
00:36:45,119 --> 00:36:48,372
Holly, mag-focus ka, okay?
Kailan mo siya nakilala?

568
00:36:48,456 --> 00:36:50,583
Pagkatapos yata ng klase.

569
00:36:50,666 --> 00:36:52,585
Okay, sa'n sa school?

570
00:36:53,502 --> 00:36:54,503
Sa library.

571
00:36:55,213 --> 00:36:56,130
Library.

572
00:37:00,593 --> 00:37:02,386
Dito 'ko dati nakatira.

573
00:37:24,283 --> 00:37:25,201
Bingo.

574
00:37:30,790 --> 00:37:32,917
Gustong-gusto ko ang librong 'yan.

575
00:37:34,752 --> 00:37:35,753
Hello.

576
00:37:36,629 --> 00:37:37,713
Ako si Henry.

577
00:37:38,631 --> 00:37:39,715
Ikaw?

578
00:37:47,223 --> 00:37:48,766
Ano ba 'to?

579
00:37:50,643 --> 00:37:51,727
Walang kuwenta.

580
00:37:54,772 --> 00:37:57,733
-Seryoso? Naglalaro ka talaga dito?
-Sinusunod lang kita.

581
00:37:58,317 --> 00:38:01,112
Sa itsura mong 'yan,
mukhang di mo nahanap 'yong generator.

582
00:38:01,195 --> 00:38:03,114
-Nandito lang 'yon.
-Pero di mo nahanap.

583
00:38:03,197 --> 00:38:04,365
Wala sa floor na 'to.

584
00:38:04,448 --> 00:38:05,533
E di mali ka.

585
00:38:06,117 --> 00:38:07,368
Tuwang-tuwa ka naman.

586
00:38:07,451 --> 00:38:09,745
Hindi, nagsasabi lang ako ng totoo.

587
00:38:09,829 --> 00:38:12,039
Hindi, nagyayabang ka, e.
Kahit na kung mali ako,

588
00:38:12,123 --> 00:38:14,959
di tayo makakapasok sa pader
at di natin mahahanap sina Holly.

589
00:38:15,042 --> 00:38:16,752
Ang selfish mo, alam mo ba 'yon?

590
00:38:16,836 --> 00:38:19,380
Ako 'yong selfish?
Gusto mo ng usapang selfish?

591
00:38:19,463 --> 00:38:21,340
No'ng nakita na natin si Hop at si El,

592
00:38:21,424 --> 00:38:24,510
iniwan natin sila para sundin
'yong bullshit na theory mo.

593
00:38:24,593 --> 00:38:27,596
Ikaw din ang dahilan kung ba't
nawalan tayo ng contact sa kanila

594
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:29,015
dahil di ka sumipot sa crawl.

595
00:38:29,098 --> 00:38:32,935
Kaya kasalanan mo 'tong gulong 'to.
At di ka man lang nag-sorry.

596
00:38:33,019 --> 00:38:35,813
Di naman sa hindi ako sumipot.
Nabugbog ako.

597
00:38:35,896 --> 00:38:38,190
Hindi, naghanap ka ng away
at 'yon ang nakuha mo.

598
00:38:38,274 --> 00:38:39,191
Tingnan mo 'yan, o.

599
00:38:39,775 --> 00:38:41,235
Marami ka na ring sablay dati,

600
00:38:41,319 --> 00:38:43,654
pero ito, ibang level ng katangahan 'to.

601
00:38:43,738 --> 00:38:44,864
Usapang katangahan ba?

602
00:38:44,947 --> 00:38:47,950
E, 'yong paghahabol mo sa syota ng iba
habang nagugunaw ang mundo?

603
00:38:48,034 --> 00:38:52,330
Kaibigan ko si Nancy.
Kaibigan ko siya, okay?

604
00:38:52,413 --> 00:38:54,874
Naaalala mo 'yong pakiramdam
ng may kaibigan?

605
00:38:54,957 --> 00:38:58,461
Oo. Naaalala ko 'yong pakiramdam
ng may mabuting kaibigan,

606
00:38:58,544 --> 00:39:02,298
'yong tunay na kaibigan
na naniniwala sa 'kin at mabait sa 'kin.

607
00:39:02,381 --> 00:39:04,050
-Huli ka!
-Ano? Ano?

608
00:39:04,133 --> 00:39:06,844
Sabi ko na nga ba.
Tungkol talaga 'to kay Eddie, e.

609
00:39:06,927 --> 00:39:09,013
Ang kabullshitan mo,
tinutulak mo kami palayo,

610
00:39:09,096 --> 00:39:11,432
wala na kasing
mas pe-perfect pa kay Eddie.

611
00:39:11,515 --> 00:39:14,101
Hindi siya perpekto,
pero alam niya 'yon, di tulad mo.

612
00:39:14,185 --> 00:39:17,438
Hindi siya peke.
Wala siyang pakialam sa sasabihin ng iba.

613
00:39:17,521 --> 00:39:19,357
Naging totoo siya sa sarili niya.

614
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:22,693
At alam mo? Siya ang pinakamatalino,
pinakamabait na taong nakilala ko.

615
00:39:22,777 --> 00:39:25,237
At kaya niyang tapusin 'to,
30 seconds sakto.

616
00:39:25,321 --> 00:39:28,616
Kung tatanga-tanga ako,
e, ba't ako 'yong nandito ngayon?

617
00:39:29,492 --> 00:39:31,327
Ano'ng gusto mong iparating?

618
00:39:31,410 --> 00:39:32,495
No'ng gabing 'yon,

619
00:39:33,871 --> 00:39:36,540
sabi ko wag kayong magpaka-hero,
sinabihan ko kayo.

620
00:39:37,249 --> 00:39:38,626
Ano'ng ginawa ni Eddie?

621
00:39:39,502 --> 00:39:41,754
-Sinugod niya 'yong mga paniki.
-Para iligtas ako.

622
00:39:41,837 --> 00:39:42,880
Wala siyang niligtas.

623
00:39:42,963 --> 00:39:45,299
-Niligtas niya tayo!
-Sabihin mo 'yan sa sarili mo.

624
00:39:45,383 --> 00:39:48,219
Kaya galit na galit ka
dahil alam mo sa sarili mo

625
00:39:48,302 --> 00:39:49,387
na 'yon ang totoo.

626
00:39:50,346 --> 00:39:52,014
Gustong magpaka-hero ni Eddie,

627
00:39:52,848 --> 00:39:56,060
pero sumablay ang plano niya
kaya namatay siya.

628
00:39:56,143 --> 00:39:57,436
Tumahimik ka!

629
00:40:00,439 --> 00:40:02,191
Wag! Ano ka ba?

630
00:40:02,274 --> 00:40:04,610
Ano ba'ng ginagawa mo? Tama na.

631
00:40:04,693 --> 00:40:07,029
Hoy! Tama na!

632
00:40:07,113 --> 00:40:09,156
Tama na! Henderson!

633
00:40:09,240 --> 00:40:12,451
Hoy! Hoy! Henderson!
Uy, ano ba'ng ginagawa mo?

634
00:40:12,535 --> 00:40:14,954
Kumalma ka! Kalma… Henderson, Henderson!

635
00:40:15,996 --> 00:40:18,374
Diyos ko! Masasaktan ka, ano ka ba!

636
00:40:23,421 --> 00:40:24,880
Okay na, Dustin.

637
00:40:28,467 --> 00:40:32,596
Tama na! Tama na! Tama na! Awat na!

638
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:38,686
Alam mo?

639
00:40:41,147 --> 00:40:42,231
Ayoko na.

640
00:40:47,736 --> 00:40:48,904
Ayoko na.

641
00:40:50,072 --> 00:40:52,700
O, sige, gumapang ka na pabalik kay Nance.

642
00:40:53,659 --> 00:40:54,577
Tanga ka.

643
00:40:55,578 --> 00:40:57,204
Peke amputa!

644
00:41:47,087 --> 00:41:48,297
Ano 'to?

645
00:41:54,678 --> 00:41:56,013
Ano kaya 'to?

646
00:41:57,097 --> 00:42:01,477
Hindi kaya nuclear explosion 'to,
parang Chernobyl?

647
00:42:02,061 --> 00:42:03,020
Oo nga.

648
00:42:03,896 --> 00:42:07,650
Naisip ko rin 'yan,
pero sa nuclear explosion,

649
00:42:08,275 --> 00:42:11,737
masusunog lahat,
hindi lang basta matutunaw.

650
00:42:13,906 --> 00:42:15,115
Napansin mo 'yong hangin?

651
00:42:16,450 --> 00:42:18,702
-'Yong hangin?
-Oo.

652
00:42:19,703 --> 00:42:20,746
Malinis, e.

653
00:42:21,288 --> 00:42:22,456
Walang spores.

654
00:42:27,586 --> 00:42:31,048
Kung anuman ang nangyari dito,
si Vecna'ng may kagagawan nito.

655
00:42:31,632 --> 00:42:32,550
Wala nang iba.

656
00:42:33,050 --> 00:42:34,301
Dark magic.

657
00:42:37,721 --> 00:42:39,056
Putang ina!

658
00:42:42,268 --> 00:42:45,187
-Okay. Okay, sige.
-Sige.

659
00:42:45,938 --> 00:42:47,940
-Ayos ka lang?
-Ayos lang ako.

660
00:42:48,023 --> 00:42:49,024
Okay.

661
00:42:50,568 --> 00:42:51,777
Diyos ko po.

662
00:42:53,612 --> 00:42:54,613
Susmaryosep.

663
00:42:55,739 --> 00:42:57,533
Ano kaya ang nangyari dito?

664
00:43:07,042 --> 00:43:09,128
Ba't ba kasi taas 'yong pinili mo?

665
00:43:30,899 --> 00:43:33,319
Di ko alam no'n
kung ga'no kalapit na 'ko sa exit.

666
00:43:33,402 --> 00:43:35,904
Pero dahil sa inyo ng pulis mo,
alam ko na.

667
00:43:38,490 --> 00:43:39,575
Ten yards.

668
00:43:40,826 --> 00:43:42,703
Ten yards.

669
00:43:43,746 --> 00:43:49,335
Isang sulok na lang pala,
mababago na 'yong buhay ko.

670
00:43:52,129 --> 00:43:53,047
Baril!

671
00:44:03,307 --> 00:44:04,850
Buksan mo 'yong pinto!

672
00:44:05,601 --> 00:44:06,727
Buksan mo 'to!

673
00:44:07,311 --> 00:44:11,190
Sa paghahanap ko ng daan palabas,
iba 'yong nahanap ko.

674
00:44:12,316 --> 00:44:14,568
Nahanap ko 'yong sagot

675
00:44:15,611 --> 00:44:18,614
kung bakit ako nando'n.

676
00:44:30,250 --> 00:44:32,086
Sinasalinan nila 'yong babae

677
00:44:33,879 --> 00:44:35,798
at 'yong dinadala niyang sanggol

678
00:44:37,383 --> 00:44:38,842
ng dugo ko.

679
00:44:42,513 --> 00:44:47,059
Unti-unti siyang pinapatay no'n,
sila ng anak niya.

680
00:44:48,977 --> 00:44:50,396
Tulong.

681
00:45:06,745 --> 00:45:10,666
Di ko alam kung ilan sila,
pero masama ang lagay nila.

682
00:45:11,458 --> 00:45:12,543
Parang mamamatay na.

683
00:45:27,474 --> 00:45:29,393
Hindi ko maintindihan.

684
00:45:30,561 --> 00:45:32,688
Mga buntis na babae.

685
00:45:34,356 --> 00:45:36,066
Secret program ng gobyerno.

686
00:45:36,150 --> 00:45:40,362
Wala ka bang naaalala do'n?

687
00:45:42,406 --> 00:45:43,407
Si Mama.

688
00:45:58,213 --> 00:46:01,467
Hindi gamot ang nagbigay sa 'tin
ng kapangyarihan, Jane.

689
00:46:02,176 --> 00:46:03,260
Si Henry.

690
00:46:08,515 --> 00:46:12,352
Sinusubukan ni Dr. Kay
na buhayin 'yong program ni Papa,

691
00:46:12,436 --> 00:46:15,564
pero di tumatalab 'yong dugo ko.

692
00:46:16,356 --> 00:46:17,775
Di gaya no'ng kay Henry.

693
00:46:18,692 --> 00:46:24,656
Ang totoo, mahinang kopya lang ni Henry
'yong mga anak ni Papa.

694
00:46:25,365 --> 00:46:26,825
Isa lang sa 'tin

695
00:46:28,035 --> 00:46:29,661
ang talagang kagaya niya.

696
00:46:30,454 --> 00:46:34,541
Ilusyon lang 'to. Hindi 'to totoo.
Walang totoo sa sinabi mo.

697
00:46:34,625 --> 00:46:37,419
Tingin mo, bakit desperado si Kay
na makuha ka?

698
00:46:37,503 --> 00:46:41,590
Hahanapin ka nila,
at gagawa sila ng maraming kagaya mo!

699
00:46:43,050 --> 00:46:44,343
Kagaya ni Henry.

700
00:46:53,727 --> 00:46:55,521
Hindi sa masaya matatapos 'to, Jane.

701
00:46:56,104 --> 00:46:57,397
Hindi para sa 'tin.

702
00:47:01,026 --> 00:47:03,278
Uy, wag kang matakot. Ako lang 'to.

703
00:47:04,112 --> 00:47:05,447
Ako lang 'to.

704
00:47:30,764 --> 00:47:32,432
Northwest. Northwest.

705
00:47:33,809 --> 00:47:35,102
Naliligaw ka na, 'no?

706
00:47:49,867 --> 00:47:51,159
Kanino galing 'tong mapa?

707
00:47:51,243 --> 00:47:52,744
Sa mama mo!

708
00:47:52,828 --> 00:47:53,996
Tumingin ka sa 'kin!

709
00:47:54,997 --> 00:47:56,790
Magsinungaling ka pa sa 'kin,

710
00:47:57,624 --> 00:48:02,379
at papatayin ko ang inutil mong tatay,

711
00:48:04,715 --> 00:48:07,384
ang ahas mong nanay,

712
00:48:10,304 --> 00:48:14,141
at ang malandi mong kapatid.

713
00:48:18,270 --> 00:48:20,480
-Okay, mga anak, tama na ang laro.
-Tara.

714
00:48:21,732 --> 00:48:22,608
Pumasok na kayo.

715
00:48:23,233 --> 00:48:25,319
Ba't ka nakasimangot?

716
00:48:25,402 --> 00:48:28,822
Magbabasa pa tayo, gagawa tayo ng art,

717
00:48:28,906 --> 00:48:31,617
at marami pa tayong matututunan.

718
00:48:34,745 --> 00:48:36,246
Sigurado kang walang nangyari

719
00:48:36,330 --> 00:48:37,956
-bago dumating 'yong Demo?
-Oo.

720
00:48:38,040 --> 00:48:39,750
Ikuwento mo nga ulit mula simula.

721
00:48:39,833 --> 00:48:41,668
-Nakuwento ko na, e.
-Ulitin mo.

722
00:48:44,087 --> 00:48:46,548
Nasa merry-go-round kami ni Mary.

723
00:48:47,132 --> 00:48:49,509
-Wag, Derek! Bitawan mo nga! Tama na!
-Kumapit ka!

724
00:48:49,593 --> 00:48:54,181
Inasar na naman kami ni Derek,
tapos tinawag ako ni Henry do'n.

725
00:48:54,264 --> 00:48:59,186
Poprotektahan daw niya 'ko sa mga halimaw,
ta's sa field ko na siya sunod na nakita.

726
00:48:59,269 --> 00:49:01,772
Napagalitan ako
sa pagkakaro'n ng imaginary friend,

727
00:49:01,855 --> 00:49:05,817
tapos nagalit si Mama
at nag-away sila ni Papa.

728
00:49:17,079 --> 00:49:18,080
Ano 'yon?

729
00:49:18,163 --> 00:49:20,666
Mali 'to. Yellow dapat 'to.

730
00:49:20,749 --> 00:49:21,750
Tama na!

731
00:49:39,184 --> 00:49:41,687
Mama! Mama!

732
00:49:41,770 --> 00:49:43,188
Mama! Papa!

733
00:49:43,271 --> 00:49:46,233
Bitawan mo 'ko, please! Bitawan mo 'ko!

734
00:49:47,901 --> 00:49:50,445
Mama! Mama! Mama!

735
00:49:50,529 --> 00:49:54,408
Tulong! Tulong, Mama! Mama! Papa!

736
00:49:57,786 --> 00:49:58,704
Umatras ka!

737
00:49:59,538 --> 00:50:00,956
Holly. Holly.

738
00:50:02,040 --> 00:50:03,000
Ayos ka lang?

739
00:50:05,085 --> 00:50:06,503
Hindi ko alam.

740
00:50:07,337 --> 00:50:08,338
Ewan. Parang…

741
00:50:08,422 --> 00:50:09,756
Natatakot ka?

742
00:50:09,840 --> 00:50:12,050
Malapit na tayo sa huling alaala.

743
00:50:13,218 --> 00:50:18,348
Posibleng maramdaman mo
'yong mga naramdaman mo no'ng gabing 'yon.

744
00:50:19,599 --> 00:50:20,767
Gano'n din ako.

745
00:50:22,853 --> 00:50:25,147
Pero parang echo lang 'yon.

746
00:50:25,814 --> 00:50:27,232
Magandang sign 'yon.

747
00:50:27,899 --> 00:50:29,818
Ibig sabihin, malapit ka nang makauwi.

748
00:50:35,032 --> 00:50:36,658
Tara. Sumunod ka sa 'kin.

749
00:50:45,083 --> 00:50:47,711
Sabi mo malapit na akong makauwi.

750
00:50:49,171 --> 00:50:51,298
Pero sasama ka, di ba?

751
00:50:52,340 --> 00:50:53,800
Hindi. Dito muna 'ko.

752
00:50:54,968 --> 00:50:57,179
Malamang. Nagpapatawa ka ba?

753
00:50:57,262 --> 00:50:58,138
Tara na.

754
00:51:03,143 --> 00:51:04,519
-Uy!
-Ano'ng ginagawa n'yo?

755
00:51:04,603 --> 00:51:05,937
Di abot sa lupa 'yong kable.

756
00:51:06,021 --> 00:51:08,857
Dito natin gagawin sa taas
'yong science experiment natin.

757
00:51:15,572 --> 00:51:16,865
Okay na.

758
00:51:16,948 --> 00:51:17,908
Mabagal lang.

759
00:51:20,243 --> 00:51:21,203
Okay.

760
00:51:23,413 --> 00:51:25,332
-Handa ka na? Handa ka na?
-Oo.

761
00:51:25,415 --> 00:51:26,708
Handa na kami!

762
00:51:48,355 --> 00:51:49,898
Okay, handa na lahat.

763
00:51:55,612 --> 00:51:58,115
Kung may mangyayari, umalis ka agad do'n.

764
00:51:58,198 --> 00:51:59,866
Opo. Promise.

765
00:51:59,950 --> 00:52:02,953
At kung magkakandaletse-letse 'to,
lalakasan namin 'yong voltage,

766
00:52:03,036 --> 00:52:06,039
susunugin namin 'yong particles,
at huhugutin namin siya sa hive.

767
00:52:08,625 --> 00:52:10,293
-Mama?
-O?

768
00:52:10,877 --> 00:52:12,671
Salamat sa pagtitiwala.

769
00:52:15,048 --> 00:52:16,758
Patayin mo 'yong tarantadong 'yon.

770
00:52:17,884 --> 00:52:19,386
Okay. Kaya mo 'to.

771
00:52:23,348 --> 00:52:24,808
Sindihan mo na, Frankenstein.

772
00:52:24,891 --> 00:52:26,726
"Fronkensteen" ang bigkas do'n!

773
00:53:07,142 --> 00:53:08,310
Gumagana.

774
00:53:08,894 --> 00:53:10,145
Gumagana!

775
00:53:10,228 --> 00:53:11,730
Nasa 50% tayo!

776
00:53:16,067 --> 00:53:17,027
Kaya mo 'yan.

777
00:53:42,093 --> 00:53:42,928
Damulag!

778
00:53:44,679 --> 00:53:46,765
Nasa'n siya? Nasa'n si Mr. Whatsit?

779
00:53:46,848 --> 00:53:48,266
Si Derek yata ako.

780
00:53:49,142 --> 00:53:51,561
-Derek?
-Kasama niya 'yong iba.

781
00:53:52,562 --> 00:53:53,980
'Yong ibang nawawalang bata.

782
00:53:54,064 --> 00:53:55,023
E, si Holly?

783
00:53:55,607 --> 00:53:57,442
-Nakikita mo ba si Holly?
-Hindi.

784
00:53:57,525 --> 00:54:01,655
Magsalita ka, damulag!
Nasa'n si Mr. Whatsit?

785
00:54:01,738 --> 00:54:03,323
Hinahanap niya si Holly.

786
00:54:03,406 --> 00:54:06,952
Hinahanap ni Henry si Holly.

787
00:54:07,035 --> 00:54:10,038
Hindi tatakas si Holly.
Hindi siya gano'n. Sinungaling ka.

788
00:54:10,121 --> 00:54:13,124
Di ako sinungaling.
Nabola siya ng halimaw.

789
00:54:13,208 --> 00:54:16,461
Naka-disguise siya na babae
na may weird na porma at pulang buhok.

790
00:54:16,544 --> 00:54:18,296
-Nagpakilala siyang…
-Max.

791
00:54:18,380 --> 00:54:20,090
Teka. Ano'ng meron kay Max?

792
00:54:20,173 --> 00:54:21,216
Kasama niya si Holly.

793
00:54:21,800 --> 00:54:24,594
Pero hinahanap sila ni Vecna.

794
00:54:35,855 --> 00:54:40,652
Nakatayo lang ako. Ba't di ako lumaban?
Ba't di ko siya tinulungan?

795
00:54:40,735 --> 00:54:43,738
'Yong dating Holly 'yon.
Lalaban ka na ngayon.

796
00:54:46,700 --> 00:54:49,953
Wag! Mama! Mama, please!

797
00:54:50,745 --> 00:54:51,746
Halika na.

798
00:55:13,685 --> 00:55:14,978
Ano 'yan?

799
00:55:16,187 --> 00:55:17,188
'Yong exit natin.

800
00:55:17,772 --> 00:55:19,774
Hindi naman mukhang exit, e.

801
00:55:25,155 --> 00:55:27,073
Sigurado ka ba na di ka halimaw?

802
00:55:27,907 --> 00:55:28,908
Sigurado ako.

803
00:55:37,667 --> 00:55:39,544
Sinabihan kita, Holly.

804
00:55:49,220 --> 00:55:50,972
Wag na wag kang pupunta sa gubat.

805
00:55:55,643 --> 00:55:58,229
-Lintik!
-Max, ayan na siya! Wag!

806
00:55:58,313 --> 00:55:59,689
Holly, akin na 'yan.

807
00:56:00,815 --> 00:56:02,359
Max, bilis!

808
00:56:29,677 --> 00:56:31,846
Sa wakas,

809
00:56:33,139 --> 00:56:35,642
nahuli na ang soro.

810
00:56:36,643 --> 00:56:38,144
Tama na!

811
00:56:51,825 --> 00:56:52,742
Max!

812
00:57:17,142 --> 00:57:18,393
Gumagana na.

813
00:57:26,401 --> 00:57:27,277
Sorcerer.

814
00:57:30,989 --> 00:57:32,907
Max! Ayos ka lang?

815
00:57:42,125 --> 00:57:43,751
-Max!
-Max!

816
00:57:43,835 --> 00:57:44,961
Kung…

817
00:57:45,044 --> 00:57:48,006
…naririnig mo ako…

818
00:57:48,089 --> 00:57:50,175
-…tumakbo…
-…ka na!

819
00:57:51,468 --> 00:57:55,680
Takbo!

820
00:58:18,119 --> 00:58:18,995
Labas.

821
00:58:20,580 --> 00:58:21,748
Labas!

822
00:58:22,957 --> 00:58:23,917
Labas!

823
00:58:25,001 --> 00:58:26,461
Ano'ng nangyayari?

824
00:58:26,544 --> 00:58:27,504
Labas!

825
00:58:28,588 --> 00:58:30,215
Labas!

826
00:58:34,719 --> 00:58:36,513
-Will, naririnig mo 'ko?
-Will! Laban!

827
00:58:36,596 --> 00:58:37,430
Nandito lang ako.

828
00:58:37,514 --> 00:58:39,724
-Laban, Will.
-Lakasan mo na!

829
00:59:06,417 --> 00:59:07,961
Will, bumalik ka sa 'min.

830
00:59:08,044 --> 00:59:09,879
Bumalik ka sa 'min, Will. Will!

831
00:59:09,963 --> 00:59:11,881
-Lintik!
-Will, bumalik ka sa 'kin!

832
00:59:11,965 --> 00:59:13,883
-Will! Will!
-Bumalik ka!

833
00:59:20,515 --> 00:59:21,516
Hala!

834
00:59:24,894 --> 00:59:26,771
Lalong dumami 'yong tunaw.

835
00:59:41,995 --> 00:59:42,996
Jonathan.

836
00:59:44,747 --> 00:59:45,873
Nakikita mo ba 'to?

837
00:59:47,917 --> 00:59:49,002
'Yong ano?

838
00:59:49,877 --> 00:59:50,878
'Yong ilaw ko.

839
00:59:51,671 --> 00:59:52,672
Panoorin mo.

840
00:59:56,467 --> 00:59:57,677
Hala.

841
01:00:09,981 --> 01:00:11,316
May kung ano do'n.

842
01:00:44,432 --> 01:00:45,767
Dark magic.

843
01:00:49,020 --> 01:00:50,021
Diyos ko.

844
01:00:52,482 --> 01:00:54,442
Dustin, Steve, copy n'yo?

845
01:00:54,525 --> 01:00:56,611
Nahanap na namin
'yong shield generator. Copy?

846
01:00:58,821 --> 01:01:00,782
Jonathan, si Dustin 'to. Copy mo?

847
01:01:00,865 --> 01:01:02,033
Di kita marinig.

848
01:01:02,116 --> 01:01:04,994
Rinig mo 'ko?
Nahanap na namin 'yong shield generator.

849
01:01:05,078 --> 01:01:07,580
Makinig ka sa 'kin.
Wag kayong gagawa ng kahit ano.

850
01:01:07,664 --> 01:01:08,873
Wag n'yong gagalawin 'yan!

851
01:01:08,956 --> 01:01:10,208
Wag n'yong galawin!

852
01:01:10,792 --> 01:01:11,668
Putik!

853
01:01:16,964 --> 01:01:18,466
Mahina 'yong signal nila.

854
01:01:20,468 --> 01:01:23,262
Puwes, mahuhuli sila sa palabas.

855
01:01:37,235 --> 01:01:38,069
Jonathan!

856
01:01:39,404 --> 01:01:41,572
Kung naririnig mo 'ko, mali ako!

857
01:01:41,656 --> 01:01:44,784
'Yong shield generator!
Hindi 'yon shield generator!

858
01:01:45,368 --> 01:01:48,121
Hindi 'yan dark magic. Iba 'yan!

859
01:01:48,204 --> 01:01:50,081
Jonathan! Nancy!

860
01:01:53,334 --> 01:01:57,839
Jonathan! Nancy!
Kung wawasakin n'yo 'yan, mamamatay kayo!

861
01:01:57,922 --> 01:02:01,342
Mamamatay tayo! Mamamatay si Holly!
Mamamatay tayong lahat!

862
01:02:01,426 --> 01:02:03,010
Copy n'yo?

863
01:02:05,263 --> 01:02:06,389
Sigurado ka ba?

864
01:02:09,559 --> 01:02:10,518
Hindi.

865
01:04:48,801 --> 01:04:50,887
Nagsalin ng Subtitle: Faith Dela Cruz

